
"Anything related to dream analysis, experience, scientific study, etc.
Esoteric ideas excluded, esoteric/\"alternative\" ideas may get classed elsewhere one day.

Lucid dreaming considered very dubious, as its scientific basis is way too limited for the kind of discussion that tends to appear around it.

For now, default is to avoid including articles about LD unless they prove to be well-grounded in reality.

With the new tentative division, dubious articles may be placed in a separate folder. However, make sure that they still fit the \"valuable\" folder. Maybe that should be renamed anyway." 